BEGIN_PGML Write an equation in the form [`f(x)=\ldots`] suggested by the pattern in the table.
>> [@DataTable( [ [[PGML('[`x`]'), rowbottom => '2', midrule => '1',], PGML('[`f(x)`]'), ], [PGML('[`[$x[0]]`]'), PGML('[`[$y[0]]`]'), ], [PGML('[`[$x[1]]`]'), PGML('[`[$y[1]]`]'), ], [PGML('[`[$x[2]]`]'), PGML('[`[$y[2]]`]'), ], [PGML('[`[$x[3]]`]'), PGML('[`[$y[3]]`]'), ], ], align => 'rl', valign => 'middle',);@]* <<
