############################################################ # Solution ############################################################
BEGIN_PGML_SOLUTION One approach to pattern recognition is to look for a relationship in each row. Here, the output value in each row is always [`10`] more than the [`x`]-value. So the pattern is described by the equation [`[$eq]\text{.}`]
